      <h2>GitHub Repository</h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/fraiseql/fraiseql-ecosystem" target="_blank">
          Visit fraiseql-ecosystem on GitHub →
        </a>
      </p>
      <p>Ecosystem documentation, strategic roadmaps, integration guides, and analysis scripts.</p>
    </section>

